{"tid":696803,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［叮噹（哆啦A夢）］靜宜（靜香）個老母一D都唔純情","createTime":"2018-06-10T11:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T13:27:29.000Z","uid":86199,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30e1b7c8f3ee5243db97fae2723923a5b341d5e2","tid":696803,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aYPm4TmtxDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaYPm4TmtxDU&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ceea44a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aYPm4TmtxDU</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集最後講到大雄留低左條底褲喺靜宜間房，靜宜老母攞返條底褲俾大雄老母。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/195825_ffbd3ec8ae8e7c3a23793b357f68589e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F195825_ffbd3ec8ae8e7c3a23793b357f68589e.png&h=be5e57b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當靜宜老母離開大雄屋企撞到返緊屋企嘅大雄，佢居然陰陰嘴笑在幾聲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/195857_7fcb83afb08dd1874f62ea6a71eca8e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F195857_7fcb83afb08dd1874f62ea6a71eca8e7.png&h=32bbb303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常老母知道有男仔喺自己個女間房連底褲都埋唔知做過d乜會係咁既反應？講緊個男仔已經小學五年級！<br />\n<br />\n靜宜老母一d都唔簡單，之前已經俾人揭發有幾個唔同嘅男人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/195434_08b1ca58b7656a65d79457337c4e8c5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F195434_08b1ca58b7656a65d79457337c4e8c5e.png&h=2546e1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邪教！？"},{"pid":"d57ce0b1254b0f1cf624575f8ff878dca1983064","tid":696803,"uid":86199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/203616_1769f3c9352e14afe7777eae0e8c3d7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F203616_1769f3c9352e14afe7777eae0e8c3d7f.png&h=53e7d99f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e8a4ba9c7fe9e014c7cd049026e392426e45430","tid":696803,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a863f4cca046534cb8d91d248eb5c99f28f55","tid":696803,"uid":24814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d57ce0b1254b0f1cf624575f8ff878dca1983064","tid":696803,"uid":86199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/203616_1769f3c9352e14afe7777eae0e8c3d7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F203616_1769f3c9352e14afe7777eae0e8c3d7f.png&h=53e7d99f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"右上果個係咪大雄老竇？"},{"pid":"f75a6a09004bf520c15bbe7299ad52fc7c85e00f","tid":696803,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ad4f31f0251420bca7e3f6894cd84ea00ef4498","tid":696803,"uid":1067,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"個女都因為職業病所以成日要沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a4df8a96b4759b7dfdeef26dd75a914addc427","tid":696803,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"其中一張圖咪靜香死咗隻狗"},{"pid":"01946354273505745a443c4c4cf0a3cba86d2fbd","tid":696803,"uid":47496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32a863f4cca046534cb8d91d248eb5c99f28f55","tid":696803,"uid":24814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d57ce0b1254b0f1cf624575f8ff878dca1983064","tid":696803,"uid":86199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"cited